{"word":"Commerce","slug":"commerce","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Commerce</b> Laws concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=19&verse=37'>Lev 19:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=25&verse=14'>Lev 25:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=25&verse=17'>Lev 25:17</a><br/> Carried on by means of caravans<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=37&verse=25'>Gen 37:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=37&verse=27'>Gen 37:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=60&verse=6'>Isa 60:6</a><br/> Carried on by means of ships<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=9&verse=28'>1Ki 9:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=10&verse=11'>1Ki 10:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=22&verse=48'>1Ki 22:48</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=107&verse=30'>Psa 107:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=31&verse=14'>Pro 31:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=18&verse=19'>Rev 18:19</a><br/> Conducted in fairs<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=27&verse=12'>Eze 27:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=27&verse=19'>Eze 27:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=11&verse=16'>Mat 11:16</a><br/> Of the:<br/> - Arabians<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=60&verse=6'>Isa 60:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=6&verse=20'>Jer 6:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=27&verse=24'>Eze 27:24</a> <br/> - Egyptians<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=42&verse=34'>Gen 42:34</a> <br/> - Ethiopians<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=4